				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "OE code to setup dialogue:\r\noe denraiddonenopeace\r\n\r\nWithout OE code:\r\nGo to Den and trigger 'plea at gates'... after this, Aradin will get into an argument with Zevlor and needs to leave. He can then be found near dead bodies beside bridge near goblin camp. Co-ordinates X:86, Y:410"
				},
